song.title: Orialcon
song.info:
by skyline june 11th, 2001.
Hot damn, this is the first serious module I've tracked since tokyo's sunset. let's see.. impulse tracker says I've been working at this for two hours and ten minutes. straight. I've never been able to sit here for more than an hour.
Boy, if it only takes me 2 hours to crank this out, I wonder what would happen if I put even more time into it :P haha. Anyway, enjoy!
